text.tspan: Domestic caloric supply, kilocalories per person per day
Total caloric domestic supply from crops,measured in average daily per capita terms (kilocalories per person per
day). These values represent crop supply after correction for trade (imports, exports & stocks), but prior to crop
allocation for alternative uses such as animal feed and industrial processes.
Source: Food system efficiency for grapher - Hannah Test
